{"tid":1766363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家支持美國 \"維吾爾人權法\"","createTime":"2019-12-02T13:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T01:02:08.000Z","uid":274996,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"be48c17ac24754141ab8140880d993e4e5c9bb20","tid":1766363,"uid":274996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T13:50:33.000Z","msg":"9月已過參議院，12月3日會上眾議院，過咗就可以俾trump 簽名。<br />\n新疆維吾爾人既情況比香港人慘1000倍，中共簡直滅絕人性，希望大家至少可以聲援維吾爾人。希望有遊行可以表達希望世界關注維吾爾人既情況，認清中共真面目<br />\n<br />\nSolomon 既tweet 都呼籲大家關心維吾爾族：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/solomonyue/status/1201493196922064896?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsolomonyue%2Fstatus%2F1201493196922064896%3Fs%3D21&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=e0f13ea0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsolomonyue%2Fstatus%2F1201493196922064896%3Fs%3D21&h=352ebba2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/solomonyue/status/1201493196922064896?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"bdc0ed41b8e26a193aad08807acf20105014f38c","tid":1766363,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T13:51:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aee89f39fb6d7c767a5d1417d695eb7db1a5d033","tid":1766363,"uid":146285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T13:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />究竟中共會讉責幾多次"},{"pid":"dba2fb9d43075f68d2d0a939a63a0750237d098f","tid":1766363,"uid":292119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T13:55:53.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"12624fce46babf929650cdbf12bcd20d7fd23a94","tid":1766363,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T13:59:21.000Z","msg":"突然間又排到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3691507d6bc919c044cce58d4b85bd283d0f7c0d","tid":1766363,"uid":33028,"like":1,"